snippet.textDisplay: This such a misrepresentation of classical music. Firstly, of course they get the most posh English person they could find and put him in a suit. Rap and classical are completely different art forms and you can't expect Kyle to notice details that JJ would have done in his song. Comparing it to classical was unnecessary in my opinion. This misrepresentation is what is causing classical music to die. People seem to think it's all quiet relaxing music for old rich people but in reality it can convey so many emotions and there's something for everyone.
